{"id": "art-1031", "label": "Art. 1031", "title": "Art. 1031", "slug": "art-1031", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_436752878\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2378\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_436752878\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 103<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1251597637\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2377\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1251597637\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Unei <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> i se permite s&#259; dobândeasc&#259;\npropriile <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, fie direct, fie prin\nintermediul unei persoane <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> în nume\npropriu, dar pe seama <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în\ncauz&#259;, cu respectarea urm&#259;toarelor <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1365166837\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2376\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1365166837\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)autorizarea dobândirii propriilor <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\neste acordat&#259; de c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; extraordinar&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, care va stabili <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nacestei dobândiri, în special num&#259;rul maxim de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nce urmeaz&#259; a fi dobândite, durata pentru care este acordat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>autoriza&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care nu\npoate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span> 18 luni de la data\nînregistr&#259;rii în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, în cazul unei dobândiri cu titlu oneros,\ncontravaloarea lor minim&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> maxim&#259;;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_652491290\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2375\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_652491290\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)valoarea nominal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nproprii dobândite de societate, inclusiv a celor aflate deja în portofoliul\ns&#259;u, nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span> 10% din capitalul\nsocial subscris;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1327309078\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2374\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1327309078\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ia</span> poate avea ca\nobiect doar <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> integral liberate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1038919582\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2373\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1038919582\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)plata <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> astfel\ndobândite se va face numai din profitul distribuibil sau din rezervele\ndisponibile ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, înscrise în\nultima <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ie</span> financiar&#259; anual&#259;\naprobat&#259;, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> rezervelor legale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_776826030\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2372\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_776826030\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>\nproprii sunt dobândite pentru a fi distribuite <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>\nastfel dobândite trebuie distribuite în termen de 12 luni de la data\ndobândirii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}